ZH: 我们正在组织一个招待会来庆祝公司成立十周年。
EN: We are organizing a reception to celebrate the company's 10th anniversary.

ZH: 他们计划在招待会上邀请各行业的专家发表演讲。
EN: They plan to invite experts from various industries to give speeches at the reception.

ZH: 明天的招待会将在大会堂举行。
EN: Tomorrow's reception will be held in the auditorium.

ZH: 这个招待会是为了感谢我们的客户对我们的支持。
EN: This reception is to thank our clients for their support.

ZH: 我们特意准备了一些小礼物，在招待会上分发给参与者。
EN: We have prepared some small gifts to distribute to the attendees at the reception.

ZH: 这个招待会很重要，所以请务必穿正式服装。
EN: This reception is important, so please be sure to wear formal attire.

ZH: 招待会上将有美食和饮料提供。
EN: There will be food and drinks provided at the reception.

ZH: 我们邀请了一支乐队来演奏音乐，让招待会更加热闹。
EN: We have invited a band to perform music and make the reception more lively.

ZH: 这个招待会将持续两个小时。
EN: This reception will last for two hours.

ZH: 我们在招待会上会提供免费的停车位。
EN: We will provide free parking spaces at the reception.

ZH: 请带上您的邀请函以便入场。
EN: Please bring your invitation letter for entry to the reception.

ZH: 招待会将从下午五点开始。
EN: The reception will start at 5 PM.

ZH: 在招待会上，我们将发布一项重要的公告。
EN: During the reception, we will make an important announcement.

ZH: 请务必在招待会上签到。
EN: Please be sure to sign in at the reception.

ZH: 招待会将举办一个抽奖活动，有机会赢得精美礼品。
EN: There will be a lucky draw at the reception, with a chance to win exquisite prizes.

ZH: 希望您能参加我们的招待会，共同庆祝这个重要的时刻。
EN: We hope you can attend our reception and celebrate this important moment together.

ZH: 为了方便组织，请您提前回复是否参加招待会。
EN: For organizational purposes, please RSVP in advance if you will attend the reception.

ZH: 如果您有任何特殊的饮食要求，请在回复中提前告知我们。
EN: If you have any special dietary requirements, please let us know in your RSVP.

ZH: 这个招待会将成为一个交流和互动的机会。
EN: This reception will be an opportunity for networking and interaction.

ZH: 招待会上将会有一个摄影师记录这个特别的时刻。
EN: There will be a photographer at the reception to capture this special moment.
